<p style="text-indent: 2.5em;">I,&#160;<u>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;<em><b>(state your name)</b></em>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;</u>&#160;do solemnly sear that I will faithfully execute the duties of dlegate to the House of Dlegates of the Chicago Teachers Union, and ill, to the best of my ability, preserve, protect, and defend the Constitution of the United States of America, the State of Illinois, the American Federation of Teachers, the Illinois Federation of Teachers, AFL-CIO, and the Chicago Teachers Union.</p>
<p style="text-indent: 2.5em;">Further, I will uphold the principles of the Chicago Teachers Union and endeavor to improve the working conditions and educational opportunities within Chicago Public Schools.</p>